frontmatter.title: Codes
frontmatter.summary: This endpoint allows the client to retreive a list of Codes.

children.value: — The Provider Id to filter by. It is the last set digits of the id.
- A list of search terms to filter by.
- Return only active codes. Defaults to true.
- Collapse NDC codes based on EPA logic.
- The field to sort the results by. Allowed: value, code
- The direction to sort the results. Allowed: asc, desc
- The first code in a range of codes
- The last code in a range of codes
